{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"张梦路","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcI0UJ2jHh6Kq7NwJg01KPhAdTxrtB27YOCDyNYflqVmOChkOmM1s8UJogTLQGWiaichDH2J1MHWWX9TCzzgwDAYgS/0","content":"<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 32px;\">父母、孩子</span><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 32px;\">如果我是父母，我会：尊重、陪伴、善待</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 32px;\">给予孩子爱的教育、美的教育、善的教育</span></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7939,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492496714000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Leo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSic0ds8BMCibGZ2OUAZx2wvLS7l0JfCujUnFH561QnYtbqvZs2sAcicsmYHVHeJSgYia20o2R8WfC0mn/0","content":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">活动策划主管与活动策划执行</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">活动策划主管：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.规划全年活动安排；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.确定每个活动是否策划，策划方向；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.与策划执行进行对接，传递活动的意义；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">4.监管活动策划与执行过程；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">5.检验最终活动成果。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">活动策划执行员（活动总控）：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.明确活动目的；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.安排团队成员各司其职；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.安排活动的宣传与招生；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">4.活动执行方案制定，物资准备；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">5.活动参与客户的服务。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7935,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492488436000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"博学笃志","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjGcyXgjKvljRv5hsGdS0pUiaecGsLTmju6ib8JdHpQwqZqXeovGLB8HRWVxBjq0BaZpicsLFdj3dfibia/0","content":"<p>&nbsp;我选择妻子的角色，<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">与我对应的那个社会角色是丈夫。对方并不明确他的角色认知，需要我帮助他澄清：</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">1、关心妻子；</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">2、照顾</span><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">孩子 ；</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">3、承担家庭经济压力‘；</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">4、承担家务。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7890,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492431818000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoPsccICKmhqibTHZ3c6PRPlXKQOMsQGCZVTGNkMa0625BIPiaGC4xAlvbRSOslvms4H38dWlfyorDL/0","content":"之前有和老板沟通过，直接领导和跨级领导，区别是直接领导更关心下属是否稳定能完成交办的事情即可，而跨级领导更专注结果","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7623,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492047434000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"锦慕兰","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaS3skBBT8HsSPCyTJe0kT5cTVYOdIHeuEGdvfS3eHvDbZuYZcRIMxiaz0lVQjiadx2BdTtgw0bzCCn0/0","content":"<p>妻子－丈夫</p><p>对丈夫角色的理解：</p><p>1）有家庭责任感：凡事以家为单位考虑，而不再以个人的喜好为主要依据。</p><p>2）有主见，有担当：家里需要做出重大决定的时候，能给出自己的意见，并结合考虑家人的意见，关键时候能拍板，并承担后果。</p><p>3）做好父母和妻子之间的沟通桥梁，有能力化解两个家庭之间的矛盾。</p><p>4）对妻子体贴，主动承担部分家务，没有大男子主义倾向；尊重孩子的选择，没有家长制的作风。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7512,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491886131000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"球状闪电","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLCPB8632Nxuia6CTs7I9LbKdkG6NPFtfP9L6Fr0dibaM7qSNgmGkpnL2Ac6YEAnVmEsBzHAbu4IicjuQ/0","content":"单身狗设想一下以后如何跟未来的老公如何沟通“丈夫”这一角色：<div>1.提问：如，他先说他自己觉得他作为老公，最终要&amp;最不重要、他做得最好&amp;最不好的，然后我谈我的看法，两相对比。</div><div>2.观察：双方父母、共同的朋友的丈夫是怎样的，对比我们自己。</div><div>3.对比：同样是职场人士，老婆我VS老公在家庭生活（如做家务、带小孩等等），不要求完全对等，但是家庭是需要双方都投入时间精力去经营的。<br><div><br></div></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7473,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491831092000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"lanlan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-09","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoABxary8VgXcewR1AmF19vgqh1yjicvfMjehwnN9BCtpicJfHXYmt3tEsP23v1u2lfVGIFicncrooia2/0","content":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 作为项目负责人，我对下属的角色认知是：</p><p>（1）参与讨论项目方案，了解项目整体框架和设计；</p><p>（2）接受研发任务，提出负责模块的详细设计和实现方法；</p><p>（3）完成模块开发，以及模块单元测试；</p><p>（4）参与整个系统的联调，进行模块的功能完善工作；</p><p>（5）提交模块开发的文档。<br><br></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7435,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491740879000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"丫头","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEpzDs95QValAW9uMicuTVwt7LGRUyD6sukUbZL6y2iaJDFgmHFGKtq1r6uWRta02dBqt8Wzyu3YPXW/0","content":"我选择的角色是妻子，与我对应的角色是丈夫<div>&nbsp;1️⃣一件事情，确保两个人同一认为范围内沟通</div><div>2️⃣针对异议，针对事情本身进行沟通，双方均表达对这件事情的看法，然后尽可能寻求双方都认可的解决方案</div><div>3️⃣尊重对方的工作，生活选择，给以充分的自由空间和选择度</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7176,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491284615000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"施伟","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-03","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEo9P2jC2S2gtzmiaPWycP2Fd6c8Lvunc8sP0iapaIrzxCur3tMr7Bia6kYfGXE4Pn3CLxmAUW8nr6ZK/0","content":"我来体验一下老板的角色，我认为我的员工要热爱工作，要不断学习知识和技术，来武装自己，习得东西都是你自己的，这一切不是给我学的，到任何地方都是你自己力量，决定你的价值，也是你值多少钱啊！","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7138,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491217855000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"迷迭香","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6bWV5FUyboCIOk2icGvegOZ7qmwDXVPlm0pmyu0tuemmkIaDqE1O6xCdX1tVMLNtwTvuVYVOMKQG3A/0","content":"我和我男朋友对他即将承担的角色（丈夫）进行了沟通，认知基本是一致的。在工作上:积极上进，为创造更好的生活奋斗。在生活上:孝敬老人，承担起“桥梁”角色，充分发挥沟通协调作用；抚养后代，承担好为人父的责任，不能把孩子推给别人撒手不管；理解和尊重妻子，给予对方信任和支持，共同面对家庭琐事，遇到问题商量着解决，能共苦可同甘。这些基本是我提出的要求，男友表示认可，想法一致。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5516,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490965666000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"王佳","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywoaJCYTv4hicL3wib7fApyhLPNJiaroIhefibZ5St8K9AWkmRhDQ3astuE22Q5cDMLXKe5anwROuryia/0","content":"父母角色。\n我认为父母\n1.应在情感上与孩子独立，不能将情感寄托在孩子身上。\n2.当孩子成家后，应经济独立，不再供给孩子，也不得干涉孩子的经济情况。\n3.心态开放，对新事物有好奇心。\n\n父母对其角色的认知：\n1.孩子即使90岁，也是孩子。\n2.自己是老古董，没能力学习新知识。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6485,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490927276000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Penny","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-30","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEvl7RszCudtn9n6PUibKnu6icMohDjZMBicUTcsawV3kw7Ah1xb0mTqIo8icMGCLicZg2nu4I9I6flbcib/0","content":"妻子对应的角色：丈夫\n\n\n妻子对丈夫的角色理解：\n\n工作和生活上可以和妻子做高质量的交流，有分歧的时候先通情后达礼；\n知道管好小家庭是顾好大家庭的最大基础和前提；\n对家庭有责任心，共同承担家庭的经济责任、育儿责任、赡养责任；重心可以略倾向于工作(如有必要)，但家庭责任仍然要力所能及的分担。\n\n\n\n丈夫自己的角色认知：\n\n丈夫主要负责物质文明；妻子主要负责精神文明。主要means 责任三七开。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6452,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490849979000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"怪盗KID","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-29","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoB2qC1jmV4KaqzhvooclkeCibFBic8ewSfkXfmoPlGFajpn0jSibyX3v8jO807ffG0FGF6f5FFRtdRM/0","content":"你是老板，和你的下属沟通你对与他所处角色的理解，看你们对下属这一角色的认知是否一致？\n\n1、提问下属，你认为你的工作岗位的职责是什么？\n2、观察下属：日常工作中的表现，是否讲重要工作放在首位？\n3、通过同事的评价侧面了解；\n4、和同期新入职的同事的工作表现做对比。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6561,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490788771000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"贾丹","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-29","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEmZHxxW6RutcFwjIMf9uz1r69ibLNmx5GBrgfLaIQKvkz0pVgu9Zlt7LqNBk6DLOrcEwVYxicVQhCj/0","content":"孩子： 与父母沟通，关于父母的角色认知他们很模糊，在孩子近30岁，应该让孩子自己做决定，但是父母的界限很模糊9","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6470,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490751065000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"郭舒简","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-28","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XRibESzncllLeNVVgOoXl3jmKXQT07IR1fYwPRIgiboTXU2tjiaAn3zpZ6cp8iaIvcTMxyrcwRR0P62w/0","content":"我的社会角色：女朋友\n男朋友眼中的他的角色认知：陪伴女朋友成长为更好的个体，帮助女朋友，保护女朋友\n和我的对男朋友的角色认知基本相符","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6192,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490685452000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"史自力","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay8CYiaFWibYsq0TUGzGLj6UOnQ45ibnxbp7iampXdnR0icJEtGrzWs09JJyRehKQG4LSf9mmdaefdPBwS/0","content":"老板:我的工作就是通过培训提升员工的工作能力，提高团队业绩！\n我:我觉得我应该是帮助员工更好的成长，使他们每个人的价值都最大化的体现出来！","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3959,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490074177000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"kerry","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5cUlGv2ibxydlESCOjsMG6yNquicDV2grtRHY4e6BREibMTu7aYqiaYHGMSVmVfneOdxIhRkLicP5at1/0","content":"帮助老板澄清社会角色\n老板从社会角度来看，要肩负一定的社会职责，比如所经营的业务必须是合法的，在此基础上能够为社会做出企业家应有的贡献和职责，一言概之：合法经营，依法纳税。我们公司是外企，这方面相当规范，这一点大家也都比较认可。\n\n从公司的角度而言，老板肩负企业发展的责任，需要拓展业务，增加业绩。目前我们公司在海外的发展都处于稳步盈利的状态，唯独大陆市场拖公司后腿，这也是客观受限导致，即我们主营业务是谷歌产品技术服务，在国内发展相对困难，目前我们还在想办法解决。\n\n老板需要管理好团队，也要承担起雇主的职责。这方面出现一些问题，即老板授权的经理人管理员工遭到大家的反对和不满，但是老板出于公司业务考虑，即便大家不满现在的经理人，仍然启用她。\n\n所以，老板在社会职责以及发展公司业务方面的工作很好，但是在授权经理人管理区域市场稍有瑕疵。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3920,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489932503000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":true},"code":200}
